y in the public domain and free to use and reuse. Disc labels that are more than 95 years old are now in the public domain and are free to use and reuse. The Library presents more recent disc labels with permission or under fair use.</p>\n<p>You are responsible for deciding whether your use of the items in this collection is legal. You will need written permission from the rightsholders to copy, distribute, or otherwise use\u00a0copyrighted materials\u00a0except as allowed by fair use or other statutory exemptions. Some materials may be protected under international law.\u00a0 You may also need permission from holders of other rights, such as publicity and/or privacy rights.\u00a0</p>\n<p>Credit Line: Library of Congress, National Jukebox.</p>\n<p>More about\u00a0<a href=\"/legal/\">Copyright and other Restrictions</a>.</p>\n<p>For guidance about compiling full citations consult\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/teachers/usingprimarysources/citing.html\">Citing Primary Sources</a>.</p>\n"], "rights_advisory": "Inclusion of the recording in the National Jukebox, courtesy of Sony Music Entertainment or EMI Music", "score": 15.245648, "shard": "01", "shelf_id": "Victor 763", "site": ["nationaljukebox"], "source_modified": "2000-01-01T12:00:00Z", "subject": ["ethnic music", "victor", "vocal"], "subject_category": ["vocal"], "subject_genre": ["ethnic music"], "subject_label": ["victor"], "subjects": [{"ethnic music": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:ethnic+music&fo=json"}, {"victor": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:victor&fo=json"}, {"vocal": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:vocal&fo=json"}], "subjects_category": [{"vocal": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/national-jukebox/?fa=subject_category:vocal&fo=json"}], "subjects_genre": [{"ethnic music": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/national-jukebox/?fa=subject_genre:ethnic+music&fo=json"}], "subjects_label": [{"victor": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/national-jukebox/?fa=subject_label:victor&fo=json